         <div xml:lang="en" type="translation">
            <ab>Ptolemaios to Zenon greeting. - - - He has sailed down(?) to obtain employment in the office of Philiskos, being recommended by Phileas and other accountants. You will do well therefore, if he is of service to you either for that or for anything else. - - -. Farewell.</ab>
